FOLDER STRUCTURE
I think structuring it as a Python package from the get-go is a good idea.

tokefx/
    tokefx/
        perturbations/
            noncanon.py
            typo.py
            __init__.py
        benchmarks/
            belebele.py
            mmlu.py
            __init__.py
        evaluate/
            tokenalignment.py
            __init__.py
        interpretability/
            <scoring_method>.py
            __init__.py
        data.py
        main.py
    scripts/
        experiments.py
        config.toml
    pyproject.toml
    README.md

